```mermaid
%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontSize': '15px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 👤 User/Client
    participant Client as 📱 Client App<br/>Browser/Mobile
    participant AuthServer as 🔐 Auth Server<br/>Identity Provider
    participant API as 🌐 API Server<br/>Resource Server
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database

    Note over User,DB: JWT 认证完整流程

    %% 登录认证阶段
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,AuthServer: 1️⃣ 用户登录认证 (Authentication)
        
        User->>Client: 输入用户名/密码
        Client->>AuthServer: POST /auth/login<br/>{ username, password }
        
        AuthServer->>DB: 查询用户信息
        DB-->>AuthServer: 返回用户记录<br/>(password_hash, salt)
        
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: 验证密码哈希
        
        alt 认证成功
            AuthServer->>AuthServer: 生成 JWT Token Pair:
            Note right of AuthServer: Access Token (15min)<br/>Refresh Token (7d)
            
            AuthServer->>AuthServer: 签名算法 (HMAC-SHA256 / RS256):
            Note right of AuthServer: Header: { alg: "HS256", typ: "JWT" }<br/>Payload: { sub, iat, exp, scope }<br/>Signature: HMACSHA256(base64(header) + "." + base64(payload), secret)
            
            AuthServer-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{ access_token, refresh_token, token_type: "Bearer", expires_in: 900 }
            Client->>Client: 安全存储 Token<br/>localStorage / Keychain / SecureStore
        else 认证失败
            AuthServer-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{ error: "invalid_credentials" }
        end
    end

    %% API 请求阶段
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,API: 2️⃣ 受保护资源访问 (Authorization)
        
        Client->>Client: 用户发起 API 请求
        Client->>Client: 从存储中读取 access_token
        
        Client->>API: GET /api/protected/resource<br/>Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
        
        API->>API: 提取并解析 JWT
        
        API->>API: 验证 Token:
        Note right of API: 1. 验证签名 (Signature)<br/>2. 检查过期时间 (exp)<br/>3. 验证发行者 (iss)<br/>4. 验证受众 (aud)<br/>5. 检查黑名单 (可选)
        
        alt Token 有效
            API->>DB: 根据 sub (user_id) 查询数据
            DB-->>API: 返回业务数据
            API-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{ data: {...} }
        else Token 过期
            API-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{ error: "token_expired" }
            Note over Client: 进入 Token 刷新流程
        else Token 无效
            API-->>Client: 403 Forbidden<br/>{ error: "invalid_token" }
        end
    end

    %% Token 刷新阶段
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,AuthServer: 3️⃣ Token 刷新 (Token Refresh)
        
        Client->>AuthServer: POST /auth/refresh<br/>{ refresh_token }
        
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: 验证 Refresh Token
        AuthServer->>DB: 检查 refresh_token 是否有效<br/>(可选: 数据库/redis 存储)
        
        alt Refresh Token 有效
            AuthServer->>AuthServer: 生成新的 Token Pair
            AuthServer-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>{ access_token, refresh_token, expires_in }
            Client->>Client: 更新存储的 Token
        else Refresh Token 过期/无效
            AuthServer-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{ error: "invalid_refresh_token" }
            Client->>User: 提示重新登录
        end
    end

    %% Token 结构说明
    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over AuthServer: 📋 JWT 结构详解
        
        Note over AuthServer: Header (Base64Url)
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: {
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "alg": "HS256",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "typ": "JWT",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "kid": "key-id-1"
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: }
        
        Note over AuthServer: Payload/Claims (Base64Url)
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: {
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "sub": "user123",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "iss": "auth.myapp.com",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "aud": "api.myapp.com",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "iat": 1704067200,
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "exp": 1704068100,
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "scope": "read write",
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   "role": "user"
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: }
        
        Note over AuthServer: Signature
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: HMACSHA256(
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   base64Url(header) + "." +
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   base64Url(payload),
        AuthServer->>AuthServer:   secret
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: )
        
        Note over AuthServer: Final JWT: base64Url(header).base64Url(payload).signature
    end

    %% 登出阶段
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,AuthServer: 4️⃣ 用户登出 (Logout)
        
        User->>Client: 点击登出
        Client->>AuthServer: POST /auth/logout<br/>Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
        
        AuthServer->>AuthServer: 将 token 加入黑名单 (可选)
        AuthServer->>DB: 删除/失效 refresh_token
        
        AuthServer-->>Client: 200 OK
        Client->>Client: 清除本地存储的 Token
        Client->>User: 返回登录页
    end

    Note over User,DB: 💡 安全最佳实践<br/>1. 使用 HTTPS 传输<br/>2. Access Token 设置短过期时间<br/>3. 安全存储 Token (避免 XSS)<br/>4. Refresh Token 轮换机制<br/>5. 使用 RS256 非对称签名 (微服务场景)
```
